race.comment: ZIPPING COLUMBUS (3) stalked the lead from a low draw then burst clear to score (26.22) at this track in a Maiden H over 460m. Looks the one to beat. MISS SPARKLES (1) proved too good on debut over 460m at this track to score by 3 lengths (26.56). Drawn to be prominent early. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. PAW TARKOV (2) has hit the frame in all of his three runs, the latest finishing second (26.54) at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. Something for the Multiples: PAW OLTRON (5)
